The Eden emulator had a recent update that completely changes the game for Snapdragon 8 Elite devices.  With the Odin 3 and KONKR Pocket Fit Elite on the way, it couldn't have come at a better time.  Here is a performance showcase with the REDMAGIC 10S Pro running the SD8 Elite Leading Version chipset.
